column2: SELECT m.*, s.bpt, s.z as sdss_z_line, s.ra as sdss_ra_line, s.dec as sdss_dec_line, s.Flux_Hb_#, s.Flux_Hb_#_err, s.Flux_OIII_#, s.Flux_OIII_#_err, s.Flux_Ha_#, s.Flux_Ha_#_err, s.Flux_NII_#, s.Flux_NII_#_err into mydb.galpair_A1#_sdss_all_Av_line_dr1# from DR1#.nocross_galpair_A1#_sdss_all_Av_line as m JOIN DR1#.emissionLinesPort AS s ON s.plate = m.sdss_plate and s.mjd = m.sdss_mjd and s.fiberid = m.sdss_fiberid
